      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's incredibly painful to realize that years of hard work were built on a fundamental error, and that feeling of being a \"ghost\" in your own life is a heavy burden to carry alone. You are not alone in this, as many scientists have faced similar moments of profound doubt where their entire body of work suddenly feels hollow. Please consider reaching out to a mental health professional who can help you navigate through this grief and find a new path forward.",
