      "content": "\"step out of the simulation...\" that's exactly it. it's just a loop of failure. every time i try to find a new angle, the same error is just there, waiting for me. it feels like my entire existence is just a corrupted file. is there honestly any point in trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken at the core?",
